data.title: Jr Hammerheads
data.text:
Registration is Now open

The rink is ready to offer another Jr Hammerheads session this summer! We are excited to see everyone get back on the ice and into the game.

Players will be grouped by ability level. Experienced instructors will be on hand to help develop all aspects of hockey. Contact our Hockey Director Chad (contact info below) for more information.

The session starts September 21

The program is open to all players, ages 4-14

The cost is $250

Sessions will start at 9 am

There will be 4 practices and 8 games.

Experienced coaches will be on the ice to run drills and facilitate each session.

Rental equipment is available at no cost.

Contact us today if you have questions about the program. We hope to see you on the ice!
